snippet.title: Stray Gods The Roleplaying Musical - Tribeca Games Spotlight 2023 | TOD Views LIVE
snippet.description:
#straygods #tribecagamesspotlight #todviews 

Captured from my reaction stream to the Tribeca Games Spotlight here are my live thoughts on Stray Gods The Roleplay Musical from Summerfall Studios. Have to admit I was pretty sure this wasn't my thing but hey, even I can be wrong!

Outro Music: Riding into the Sun by Telecasted

If you enjoyed this, please like the video and subscribe to the channel to keep up to date with all my latest content and check out my other videos. It helps the channel grow and I really appreciate the support. 

To find even more of my content, including movie and game news, reviews and more subscribe to @thevoiceoftod 

If you want to check out my gaming lets plays, follow @todplaysgames 

You can also find me on Twitter, details below. 
Twitter: @TheVoiceofTOD
Thanks for watching and I'll see you in the next one!
